OL,3,CResidents blocked from long-term
OL,4,Cillness payments due to year of birth
OL,6,FJersey residents are calling for a
OL,7,Fchange in how disability benefits are
OL,8,Foffered after they were blocked from
OL,9,Flong-term illness or injury financial
OL,10,Fsupport (LTIA) due to the year they
OL,11,Fwere born.
OL,13,FThose who are eligible can receive a
OL,14,Fmaximum of #265.93 in government
OL,15,Ffunding a week.
OL,17,FHowever, current legislation means
OL,18,Fpeople born or diagnosed with a long-
OL,19,Fterm illness before 1 October 2004
OL,20,Fcannot claim the benefit.
