OL,3,CResidents blocked from long-term
OL,4,Cillness payments due to year of birth
OL,6,FTania Angell, 58, was born deaf and
OL,7,Fdiagnosed at the age of three but has
OL,8,Fonly recently discovered financial
OL,9,Fsupport exists.
OL,11,FAfter following up on her allowance
OL,12,Fapplication, Tania was told she did
OL,13,Fnot meet the threshold as her
OL,14,Fdiagnosis came before 2004.
OL,16,FShe explains: "I was just astounded
OL,17,Fthat this could happen in this day and
OL,18,Fage.
