OL,3,CResidents blocked from long-term
OL,4,Cillness payments due to year of birth
OL,6,F"It has to be fair and equal to all
OL,7,Fand accessible to all but people need
OL,8,Fto know about it.
OL,10,F"I've got to this age and I've never
OL,11,Fknown about it, and I just felt it was
OL,12,Freally unfair."
OL,14,FPilates teacher Tania Le Couilliard,
OL,15,F45, is also deaf and cannot claim
OL,16,Ffinancial support either as she was
OL,17,Fdiagnosed at five years old.
