OL,3,CResidents blocked from long-term
OL,4,Cillness payments due to year of birth
OL,6,FShe says that the allowance could have
OL,7,Fhelped her afford specialist equipment
OL,8,Fsuch as accessories to hear phone
OL,9,Fcalls or computer audio.
OL,11,FTania explains: "That extra bit of
OL,12,Fmoney would have gone a long way to be
OL,13,Fable to afford to make my life a lot
OL,14,Feasier in the long run.
OL,16,F"It would certainly help me to feel
OL,17,Flike I don't have to work as much if I
OL,18,Fhad that extra bit of support.
OL,19,FMentally, it would take a huge stress
OL,20,Foff the shoulders."
