OL,6,FJersey's Social Security Minister
OL,7,FDeputy Lyndsay Feltham has previously
OL,8,Fsaid that the government benefit is
OL,9,Fnot in line with the practices of
OL,10,Fother countries such as the UK.
OL,12,FShe adds: "When it came about, there
OL,13,Fwere different views around disability
OL,14,Fand incapacity at the time and we need
OL,15,Fto do some work to ensure that they
OL,16,Fbecome more modern and fit for purpose.
OL,18,F"I'm aware that currently, the testing
OL,19,Ffor LTIA is a quite difficult process
OL,20,Ffor people and we need to make that
OL,21,Fprocess better.
