OL,3,CResidents blocked from long-term
OL,4,Cillness payments due to year of birth
OL,6,F"The only way we can do that is by
OL,7,Fchanging the legislation ... It has to
OL,8,Fbe fair, equal, and accessible to all."
OL,10,FDeputy Feltham says that work to
OL,11,Fmodernise benefit rules will not start
OL,12,Funtil early 2025.
OL,14,FShe explains that the main focus this
OL,15,Fyear was on income support but that
OL,16,Fshe will speak to individuals who feel
OL,17,Fthey have been let down by the system
OL,18,Fto work out what legislative gaps need
OL,19,Faddressing.
